column5: Well it was good that you got out at least and caught a nice one! It looks like you enjoyed yourself!   Merry xmas Greencoachdog!
You'd do much better if you were wearing 'the' sweater, Glenner, you should know that by now....  Still, nice l'il guys nonetheless....
Well glen good for you at least you did'nt get skunked.2 weekends in arow for me skunked both times.  Merry Christmas and take care of your Pop.Mike
Good for you getting out Glen! A couple of small fish are better than none!  Took one for the team stayed home and helped around the house.  Whopper

Good stuff Glen, nice to get away for a bit, especially when things have been a bit rough, need to recharge, and there ain't no better way  I hope to go for a bit on Thurs. might take a couple of young one's to try out their new fishing gear  Maureen
...say Glen small dinks are better than none,at least you got out and caught something insted of getting SKUNKED wtg bud take care.  Steve
Glen, For a moment there I thought you were holdin a muskie bait  Cheers !!!
You could of put it back on the hook and traded it for a Striper.....   Nice trip though.  Art
